name: Brickbreak-cs3360
tagline: Co-op assingment to create a simple brick breaker game
body:
### Welcome to Brick Breaker.
This is a simple android app that allows you break bricks with prejudice.

### Authors and Contributors
This app is created by a group of three CS majors at Troy University. This project is lead by @docpasma, with awesome support from two other devs.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with the app, site, or any questions? Hit up @docplasma to resolve any issue.
